215-1"&gt;SAP Business Technology Platform&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+S%25252F4HANA+Cloud+Public+Edition/pd-p/08e2a51b-1ce5-4367-8b33-4ae7e8b702e0" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="1199-1"&gt;SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
